      "last_action_date": "2011-12-01",
      "last_action": "Carried over to 2012 Regular Session.",
      "title": "Youth Sports; Head Injuries",
      "description": "Requires the department of education to adopt rules to educate coaches, youth athletes, and their parents or guardians of the nature and risk of concussions and head injuries. Requires that coaches receive annual training to recognize symptoms of concussions and that youth athletes suspected of sustaining a concussion be kept from practice or competition until conditions are met."
