      "last_action": "Carried over to 2012 Regular Session.",
      "title": "Homeless Job Training Program; DLIR; Appropriation",
      "description": "Establishes a homeless job training program to be managed by the Department of Labor and Industrial Relations. Requires the Department of Labor and Industrial Relations to seek federal funds that are intended for the homeless or other funds that may be available in accordance with the homeless job training program. Appropriates funds. Effective July 1, 2011. (HB1450 HD1)"
