      "title": "Hawaii Employer-Union Health Benefits Trust Fund; Retiree Reserves",
      "description": "Prohibits the use of funds in a reserve fund created to be used as a reserve against the Hawaii Employer-Union Health Benefits Trust Fund's future costs of providing health and other benefits plans for retirees to be used to pay for health or other benefit plans for active employees."
