      "last_action": "Carried over to 2012 Regular Session.",
      "title": "Impact Fees; Exemption for Urban Core",
      "description": "Prohibits counties from imposing impact fees for any development, or portion thereof, conducted within an urban core. Defines \"urban core\" as an urbanized area that has a population density of at least 1,000 people per square mile and a total area population of more than 20,000 people."
