      "last_action_date": "2012-01-25",
      "last_action": "(S) Referred to JDL.",
      "title": "Child Abuse",
      "description": "To provide greater protection to our children, this bill amends the offense of promoting child abuse in the second degree to include the possession of particularly violent or egregious child pornography."
